{"tid":583240,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"ex開會時嘔血入左院","createTime":"2018-03-06T23:48:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T00:59:11.000Z","uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"74680d47330f01c46d4548fc291b2955806e1ea9","tid":583240,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T23:48:16.000Z","msg":"話說ex就係舊上司<br />\n公司幾千人都係聽佢order<br />\n因工作多磨擦而分手 後來我轉埋工<br />\n<br />\n辭職前佢做咗好多野去折磨我<br />\n心裏面好憎好憎佢 覺得佢會有報應<br />\n<br />\n最近證明左工作爭拗 我啱佢錯<br />\n後果好大鑊 唔好彩幾千無左份工<br />\n好彩都要響一個月間炒左幾百人<br />\n炒既仲要好多係佢親自邀請join<br />\n<br />\n佢本身身體唔好<br />\n仲要因爲今次壓力大 攪到高血壓<br />\n幾次開會其間頂唔順中止 即刻去醫院<br />\n噚晚開開下會嘔血 之後嚮屋企暈要call白車<br />\n返到去弱雞到要人幫先落到車<br />\n到出大function又扮無事照俾人&rdquo;對&rdquo;紅酒茅台<br />\n<br />\n有d好黑心既被炒同事話佢呢d係報應<br />\n&ldquo;that&rsquo;s what he get for screwing peoples&rsquo; life&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n唉 原來睇佢有報應係唔會令人釋放仇恨<br />\n公司不嬲都好政治化<br />\n好多人平時笑騎騎但都係等插佢一刀<br />\n諗起佢沉默寡言 一個面對咁多壓力都好慘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182c3db2458ea528409b64e7447d74535b03c9ba","tid":583240,"uid":6103,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T23:51:52.000Z","msg":"佢自己囉黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都識講你臨走前佢點對你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔需要同情呢種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea818448af689f64b1b87d4984e0107e4e60cca","tid":583240,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T23:52:44.000Z","msg":"咸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73cabd0766caae6e64f9a3c71e27e5eb7091fd52","tid":583240,"uid":38946,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T23:58:38.000Z","msg":"保險狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643d991904dc4731f4648d0426189e9